WEBVTT

﻿1
00:00:06.000 --> 00:00:12.074
Watch Online Movies and Series for FREE
www.osdb.link/lm

2
00:00:48.518 --> 00:00:52.404
In the early Northern Song dynasty. the country
was often invaded by the Khitan-led Liao Dynasty.

3
00:00:52.405 --> 00:00:55.756
The former Yan kingdom's old forces were
secretly planning to restore their power.

4
00:00:55.757 --> 00:00:58.736
Territorial disputes triggered wars.
Kindness and enmity were everywhere.

5
00:00:58.737 --> 00:01:01.999
Love and hatred were all ignited by greed
and jealously. No one was an exception.

6
00:01:02.000 --> 00:01:03.917
Those who had feelings
were all caught in them.

7
00:01:35.517 --> 00:01:37.851
Mother. do you see how tall I have grown?

8
00:01:37.852 --> 00:01:39.101
- Let me see.
- You little brat.

9
00:01:39.102 --> 00:01:41.141
- You're up to here.
- You're almost as tall as me.

10
00:01:41.142 --> 00:01:42.352
That's right.

11
00:02:47.559 --> 00:02:50.308
He's fine. He's back!

12
00:02:50.309 --> 00:02:51.267
He's all right.

13
00:02:51.268 --> 00:02:53.727
How many Liao thieves did you kill today?

14
00:02:56.683 --> 00:02:58.683
Buddy. aren't you afraid of death?

15
00:02:58.684 --> 00:03:01.766
As a Beggars' Gang disciple.
we live and die together. of course.

16
00:03:01.767 --> 00:03:03.476
Kid. you are capable.

17
00:03:03.477 --> 00:03:05.516
I. Ma Dayuan. won't be wrong about him.

18
00:03:05.517 --> 00:03:06.933
This is my woman.

19
00:03:06.934 --> 00:03:08.391
Greet Qiao.

20
00:03:08.392 --> 00:03:09.601
Qiao.

21
00:03:09.602 --> 00:03:11.808
Elder Xi. are you all right?

22
00:03:11.809 --> 00:03:13.067
Yes. I'm fine.

23
00:03:20.852 --> 00:03:22.083
East five. south three.

24
00:03:23.392 --> 00:03:24.513
Five. six. eight.

25
00:03:25.559 --> 00:03:26.559
Gusu.

26
00:04:06.851 --> 00:04:08.808
Waiter. is breakfast available yet?

27
00:04:08.809 --> 00:04:10.141
Hurry up and bring us some.

28
00:04:10.142 --> 00:04:11.977
Sure. Please come with me.

29
00:04:26.352 --> 00:04:29.642
Master. what is in your cage downstairs?

30
00:04:30.391 --> 00:04:31.726
A sacrifice.

31
00:04:31.727 --> 00:04:33.247
So it's livestock.

32
00:04:34.625 --> 00:04:37.601
My compassionate Buddha
does not abandon any sentient beings.

33
00:04:37.602 --> 00:04:40.332
I was passing through Dali
when I met a stubborn creature.

34
00:04:40.333 --> 00:04:48.333
It was unruly. so I'm bringing it
to an old friend as a sort of deliverance.

35
00:04:48.637 --> 00:04:49.805
Take your time.

36
00:04:52.658 --> 00:04:55.099
Rehabilitating others is
easy. oneself less so.

37
00:04:55.991 --> 00:04:58.032
You are a monk.

38
00:04:58.033 --> 00:05:01.157
A monk should speak of compassion.

39
00:05:01.158 --> 00:05:05.408
If you are compassionate.
why do you cage a living human being?

40
00:05:17.161 --> 00:05:18.666
Brave sir. I'm Duan Yu of Dali!

41
00:05:18.667 --> 00:05:21.880
This vile monk. Jiu Mozhi. will sacrifice
me at Murong Bo's tomb in Gusu...

42
00:05:40.990 --> 00:05:43.658
I would like to ask you. Master.
What is compassion?

43
00:05:45.241 --> 00:05:49.740
Compassion brings happiness to all beings
and plucks all beings from suffering.

44
00:05:49.741 --> 00:05:53.907
I send him to be redeemed.
naturally. to save him from suffering.

45
00:05:53.908 --> 00:05:56.741
Forcing someone to be redeemed
will increase his suffering.

46
00:05:58.325 --> 00:05:59.657
How is that compassion?

47
00:05:59.658 --> 00:06:02.407
Three lifetimes of karma
and six paths of reincarnation.

48
00:06:02.408 --> 00:06:05.490
I'm redeeming the caged person.

49
00:06:05.491 --> 00:06:09.033
It is to help him redeem his karma
and return to reincarnation.

50
00:06:10.532 --> 00:06:12.157
Is that not compassion?

51
00:06:12.158 --> 00:06:13.497
Destiny let us meet.

52
00:06:14.866 --> 00:06:17.032
I met you by chance.

53
00:06:17.033 --> 00:06:18.907
It is quite a fate.

54
00:06:18.908 --> 00:06:20.033
How about this?

55
00:06:21.158 --> 00:06:24.115
This meal is on me.

56
00:06:24.116 --> 00:06:27.283
But the young man in the
cage has to stay today.

57
00:06:31.325 --> 00:06:34.365
It seems that this was
not a chance meeting.

58
00:06:34.366 --> 00:06:35.576
Sir.

59
00:06:36.749 --> 00:06:38.791
you have been waiting here for a while.

60
00:06:40.283 --> 00:06:43.157
I journeyed from Tubo
and am just passing through here.

61
00:06:43.158 --> 00:06:45.033
I did not capture one of the Song people.

62
00:06:46.036 --> 00:06:47.740
What does it have to do with you?

63
00:06:47.741 --> 00:06:53.247
In the land of the Great Song. anyone who
disregards morality becomes my business.

64
00:06:53.248 --> 00:06:56.240
There is too much bad karma in the world.

65
00:06:56.241 --> 00:06:58.951
I advise you not to play with fire.

66
00:07:00.326 --> 00:07:03.865
I'm just a man who can't afford warm
clothes and can't get enough to eat.

67
00:07:03.866 --> 00:07:05.201
I'm not afraid of bad karma...

68
00:07:06.375 --> 00:07:11.615
as long as I can face the heavens without
shame and live up to people's expectations.

69
00:07:11.616 --> 00:07:15.615
The Song dynasty is in jeopardy.

70
00:07:15.616 --> 00:07:19.575
If you know what is good for you.
you should leave the state.

71
00:07:19.576 --> 00:07:23.289
Perhaps you will have a chance to survive.

72
00:07:23.290 --> 00:07:26.915
Aren't you afraid of being
surrounded by enemies?

73
00:07:27.948 --> 00:07:30.208
Don't incur the wrath of the masses!

74
00:07:31.083 --> 00:07:32.875
I won't offend you if you don't offend me.

75
00:07:36.000 --> 00:07:38.957
If someone offends me and crosses the line.

76
00:07:38.958 --> 00:07:40.874
I'll fight with him.

77
00:07:40.875 --> 00:07:43.417
I'll fight as long as he wants.

78
00:07:43.418 --> 00:07:45.083
I'll keep on fighting.

79
00:07:48.125 --> 00:07:49.375
Then...

80
00:07:50.583 --> 00:07:53.793
we shall test your luck today.

81
00:08:06.958 --> 00:08:08.375
Dragon Claw Hand.

82
00:10:00.708 --> 00:10:02.625
- Dog Beating Staff?
- It's used on jerks.

83
00:10:27.293 --> 00:10:31.124
Since you came from Tubo. you may not
have adjusted to the Central Plain.

84
00:10:31.125 --> 00:10:33.417
We are tolerant after all.

85
00:10:33.418 --> 00:10:35.418
Would you like to take a
breath before continuing?

86
00:11:29.833 --> 00:11:33.832
If you want to save all beings in hell. you
must first endure the suffering of hell!

87
00:11:33.833 --> 00:11:37.000
Until hell is empty. you
will not become a Buddha!

88
00:11:46.083 --> 00:11:48.333
Go to hell!

89
00:12:25.668 --> 00:12:27.958
Eighteen Subduing Dragon Palms?

90
00:12:48.293 --> 00:12:50.125
- Greetings. Master!
- Greetings. Master!

91
00:12:53.208 --> 00:12:56.500
You are the master of the
Beggars' Gang. Qiao Feng.

92
00:14:40.418 --> 00:14:42.749
What's the occasion? Why is everyone here?

93
00:14:42.750 --> 00:14:46.793
Qiao Feng. something big has happened
in the Beggars' Gang.

94
00:14:49.333 --> 00:14:52.332
Sir. the Beggars' Gang has
no relationship with our Murong family.

95
00:14:52.333 --> 00:14:53.667
Why did you bring us here?

96
00:14:53.668 --> 00:14:58.417
I just want you to see
the reality of the Beggars' Gang.

97
00:14:58.418 --> 00:15:03.208
known as the first largest gang of beggars
in the world.

98
00:15:06.632 --> 00:15:09.425
Within our gang is a foreign traitor.

99
00:15:10.315 --> 00:15:14.215
And this traitor holds a
high status in the gang.

100
00:15:15.125 --> 00:15:17.333
The traitor we are talking about...

101
00:15:18.958 --> 00:15:20.624
is you.

102
00:15:20.625 --> 00:15:23.000
- What did you say?
- What are you talking about?

103
00:15:30.333 --> 00:15:32.875
Elder Bai. what do you mean to say?

104
00:15:34.083 --> 00:15:36.180
Vice Master Ma was killed last night...

105
00:15:37.583 --> 00:15:38.874
by a traitor.

106
00:15:38.875 --> 00:15:40.874
Vice Master Ma was killed?

107
00:15:40.875 --> 00:15:42.167
What happened?

108
00:15:42.168 --> 00:15:44.667
Someone testified that you did it.

109
00:15:44.668 --> 00:15:46.417
That's ridiculous!

110
00:15:46.418 --> 00:15:48.833
I had no enmity with him.
Why would I hurt him?

111
00:15:50.875 --> 00:15:52.043
What happened?

112
00:15:57.418 --> 00:15:58.418
Who said that?

113
00:16:04.047 --> 00:16:05.125
It was me.

114
00:16:13.083 --> 00:16:14.083
Qiao Feng.

115
00:16:15.708 --> 00:16:18.792
Why did you kill my husband?

116
00:16:18.793 --> 00:16:22.083
Mrs. Ma. don't let anyone
sow discord between us.

117
00:16:22.875 --> 00:16:25.168
My husband told me before he died.

118
00:16:26.293 --> 00:16:30.750
He said he had a letter
that could reveal your true identity.

119
00:16:31.875 --> 00:16:35.043
He was afraid you would
kill him to silence him.

120
00:16:35.044 --> 00:16:36.294
He also said...

121
00:16:38.708 --> 00:16:42.250
that if one day he really was killed.

122
00:16:43.543 --> 00:16:45.333
it would be you who did it.

123
00:16:47.250 --> 00:16:48.708
Please. Elder Bai.

124
00:16:51.125 --> 00:16:57.000
Please read the contents of the letter
to the gang's brothers.

125
00:17:01.917 --> 00:17:06.124
"This man. Qiao Feng. is not one of us.

126
00:17:06.125 --> 00:17:11.457
His biological parents died
at the hands of the Song people.

127
00:17:11.458 --> 00:17:15.874
All will be fine if this boy
does not know his origins.

128
00:17:15.875 --> 00:17:19.292
Otherwise. not only will the Beggars' Gang
be destroyed at his hands.

129
00:17:19.293 --> 00:17:24.207
but the Central Plain
will also suffer a great calamity.

130
00:17:24.208 --> 00:17:28.457
There is too much at stake
when choosing the next gang master.

131
00:17:28.458 --> 00:17:31.458
"Please think twice."

132
00:17:45.668 --> 00:17:47.000
Just based on this letter?

133
00:17:47.001 --> 00:17:52.049
There may still be doubts
that you murdered Vice Master Ma.

134
00:17:52.050 --> 00:17:56.374
However. you are a Khitan.

135
00:17:56.375 --> 00:17:59.833
Not only do we have physical evidence.
but we also have witnesses.

136
00:18:02.208 --> 00:18:03.750
Elder Xu is here!

137
00:18:05.833 --> 00:18:08.333
- Greetings. Elder Xu.
- Greetings. Elder Xu.

138
00:18:12.875 --> 00:18:19.832
Thirty years ago. one of our leading brothers
led the great heroes of the Central Plain

139
00:18:19.833 --> 00:18:24.874
to Yanmen Pass to ambush Khitan soldiers.

140
00:18:24.875 --> 00:18:27.707
Master Wang was among them.

141
00:18:27.708 --> 00:18:34.332
At the time. a Khitan couple mistakenly entered
the battlefield and unfortunately died.

142
00:18:34.333 --> 00:18:37.458
leaving behind a baby in swaddling clothes.

143
00:18:38.293 --> 00:18:42.499
This child grew up and
joined the Beggars' Gang.

144
00:18:42.500 --> 00:18:45.416
He made great achievements in battle.

145
00:18:45.417 --> 00:18:53.332
Master Wang then intended to pass on the
position of master of the Beggars' Gang to him.

146
00:18:53.333 --> 00:18:58.499
This letter was written
by the leading brother to Master Wang.

147
00:18:58.500 --> 00:19:05.168
At the end of Master Wang's life.
he gave this letter to Vice Master Ma.

148
00:19:06.918 --> 00:19:11.167
Qiao Feng. we have witnesses
and physical evidence.

149
00:19:11.168 --> 00:19:14.833
The evidence is irrefutable.
What do you have to say?

150
00:19:16.125 --> 00:19:17.125
Elder Xu.

151
00:19:18.543 --> 00:19:19.543
take care.

152
00:19:25.375 --> 00:19:29.542
Have you considered that
this letter could be forged?

153
00:19:29.543 --> 00:19:33.374
Whether Elder Xu's words are true or not.
I'll definitely find out.

154
00:19:33.375 --> 00:19:35.917
For the sake of
the Beggars' Gang's 100-year foundation.

155
00:19:35.918 --> 00:19:41.582
we must first depose you as a gang master
and expel you from the Beggars' Gang.

156
00:19:41.583 --> 00:19:46.167
We will never allow a Khitan
to continue to be our master!

157
00:19:46.168 --> 00:19:47.999
Disciples.

158
00:19:48.000 --> 00:19:51.430
If you still persist in ignorance.
you'll be punished according to our rules.

159
00:19:59.843 --> 00:20:01.093
Elders.

160
00:20:01.958 --> 00:20:03.458
today.

161
00:20:04.625 --> 00:20:09.624
are you certain you wish
to depose Qiao Feng as a master?

162
00:20:09.625 --> 00:20:11.792
As the Discipline Elder.

163
00:20:11.793 --> 00:20:16.167
I must remind you
that according to the gang's rules.

164
00:20:16.168 --> 00:20:19.499
disciples that offend the gang master.

165
00:20:19.500 --> 00:20:21.624
regardless of the reason.

166
00:20:21.625 --> 00:20:25.583
must be subjected to disciplinary daggers
to offset the crime of disrespect.

167
00:20:26.958 --> 00:20:28.254
Bring the daggers.

168
00:20:31.125 --> 00:20:34.832
A great man has no fear of death.
let alone a mere disciplinary dagger.

169
00:20:34.833 --> 00:20:35.833
I'll go first!

170
00:20:39.083 --> 00:20:40.375
What are you doing?

171
00:20:40.376 --> 00:20:41.754
You four elders...

172
00:20:43.917 --> 00:20:45.624
are meritorious members of the gang.

173
00:20:45.625 --> 00:20:48.624
We are all brothers. I don't wish to fight.

174
00:20:48.625 --> 00:20:50.504
Allow me to bear this
corporal punishment...

175
00:20:52.543 --> 00:20:53.708
in your place.

176
00:20:54.750 --> 00:20:56.168
- Master!
- Master!

177
00:21:01.250 --> 00:21:02.590
A great man...

178
00:21:04.667 --> 00:21:08.042
acts with integrity and honesty
and has nothing to be ashamed of.

179
00:21:09.375 --> 00:21:10.375
All right.

180
00:21:15.625 --> 00:21:19.458
From this moment on.
I'm no longer the Beggars' Gang's master.

181
00:21:24.668 --> 00:21:26.499
Listen up.

182
00:21:26.500 --> 00:21:31.542
I'll find out the truth
behind all the slander against me today.

183
00:21:31.543 --> 00:21:32.874
Don't worry. everyone.

184
00:21:32.875 --> 00:21:36.250
I'll never harm a single
Song life as long as I live.

185
00:21:37.000 --> 00:21:38.000
Take care.

186
00:21:38.750 --> 00:21:39.750
Stop.

187
00:21:41.000 --> 00:21:45.125
You killed my husband.
Do you want to get away with it?

188
00:21:45.875 --> 00:21:49.874
Qiao Feng. you are no
longer the gang master.

189
00:21:49.875 --> 00:21:53.418
That means we can punish
you as an outsider.

190
00:21:54.125 --> 00:21:57.293
If I wish to leave. who can stop me?

191
00:22:06.043 --> 00:22:07.916
I think Qiao Feng is a foolish man.

192
00:22:07.917 --> 00:22:11.874
He has kung fu skills. but he lets
the Beggars' Gang bully him to this extent.

193
00:22:11.875 --> 00:22:15.957
If it were me.
I would've taught those ingrates a lesson.

194
00:22:15.958 --> 00:22:19.750
That's right. He even took
the punishment for them. What a joke.

195
00:22:21.083 --> 00:22:23.293
Azhu. what do you think?

196
00:22:26.708 --> 00:22:29.332
This world has all kinds of people.

197
00:22:29.333 --> 00:22:32.374
Some bite the hand that feeds them.
Some repay grievances with virtue.

198
00:22:32.375 --> 00:22:33.749
It's all a matter of the heart.

199
00:22:33.750 --> 00:22:38.257
I think Qiao Feng is not foolish.
He is just seeking a guilt-free heart.

200
00:22:39.668 --> 00:22:43.542
Loyalty and righteousness are inconstant.
Heaven and earth are not benevolent.

201
00:22:43.543 --> 00:22:46.749
Since ancient times. loyalty and
righteousness are engraved on memorials

202
00:22:46.750 --> 00:22:49.167
while profit and wealth move the heart.

203
00:22:49.168 --> 00:22:51.708
Azhu. go to Shaolin Temple.

204
00:23:07.125 --> 00:23:09.793
- Come catch me.
- Stop! I'll catch you.

205
00:24:16.208 --> 00:24:17.208
Father!

206
00:24:18.000 --> 00:24:19.000
Mother!

207
00:24:23.750 --> 00:24:24.750
Father.

208
00:24:27.750 --> 00:24:28.833
I'm Qiao Feng.

209
00:24:35.708 --> 00:24:36.793
Who did this?

210
00:24:48.500 --> 00:24:50.249
I want to know.

211
00:24:50.250 --> 00:24:52.708
- Who am I?
- You are...

212
00:25:05.168 --> 00:25:07.333
Mr. Qiao. we've come to harvest seedlings.

213
00:25:10.833 --> 00:25:12.249
Qiao Feng!

214
00:25:12.250 --> 00:25:13.999
You killed your parents?

215
00:25:14.000 --> 00:25:19.042
That must mean the rumor that you killed
the Beggars' Gang's Ma Dayuan is true!

216
00:25:19.043 --> 00:25:22.332
You really are a Khitan bastard!
You're worse than animals!

217
00:25:22.333 --> 00:25:26.375
If you are capable. you can
try to kill us both today!

218
00:25:30.926 --> 00:25:32.466
I didn't kill anyone.

219
00:25:34.083 --> 00:25:35.708
If I were to kill someone.

220
00:25:37.333 --> 00:25:39.083
would you still be alive?

221
00:25:45.000 --> 00:25:53.000
[In Loving Memory Of My
Parents. Mr. And Mrs. Qiao]

222
00:25:56.708 --> 00:25:58.832
Who really injured you?

223
00:25:58.833 --> 00:26:02.833
Do you truly refuse to say anything?

224
00:26:09.293 --> 00:26:11.583
The day I was ordained.

225
00:26:13.333 --> 00:26:15.918
my master named me...

226
00:26:17.668 --> 00:26:20.042
Xuanku.

227
00:26:20.043 --> 00:26:22.168
Unfortunately. in life.

228
00:26:23.375 --> 00:26:25.583
the sea of suffering is endless.

229
00:26:26.750 --> 00:26:31.417
I cannot help the one who hurt me.

230
00:26:31.418 --> 00:26:35.249
so there is nothing to say.

231
00:26:35.250 --> 00:26:40.458
Xuanku. why must you suffer like this?

232
00:26:40.459 --> 00:26:42.251
I don't want...

233
00:26:44.668 --> 00:26:51.542
any of you to worry about me.

234
00:26:51.543 --> 00:26:53.918
further increasing my karmic debt.

235
00:26:55.000 --> 00:26:59.043
I do not say anything in hopes that...

236
00:26:59.958 --> 00:27:01.418
that man...

237
00:27:03.043 --> 00:27:10.168
can put down the butcher's
knife and repent his ways.

238
00:28:07.333 --> 00:28:08.375
Master.

239
00:28:11.958 --> 00:28:13.583
I. Qiao Feng. am useless.

240
00:28:15.208 --> 00:28:17.208
I have shamed Shaolin's reputation.

241
00:28:21.793 --> 00:28:26.043
I have come tonight to see you
for clarification on one thing.

242
00:28:31.543 --> 00:28:33.208
Am I a Song man...

243
00:28:36.500 --> 00:28:38.168
or a Khitan?

244
00:28:57.668 --> 00:28:58.708
Master.

245
00:29:05.749 --> 00:29:08.292
Help! That man is back again!

246
00:29:08.293 --> 00:29:09.293
Quickly. help!

247
00:29:09.294 --> 00:29:11.419
Help! That man is back again!

248
00:29:35.125 --> 00:29:36.708
- Xuanku!
- Xuanku!

249
00:29:39.583 --> 00:29:41.293
Find him!

250
00:29:42.083 --> 00:29:44.418
Amitābha.

251
00:30:11.543 --> 00:30:13.999
You said I'm back again. What do you mean?

252
00:30:14.000 --> 00:30:15.582
Have you seen me before?

253
00:30:15.583 --> 00:30:17.437
The Tendon-Altering Sutra has been stolen!

254
00:30:19.583 --> 00:30:21.049
[Tendon-Altering Sutra]

255
00:30:21.050 --> 00:30:22.507
There is someone in this room!

256
00:30:26.625 --> 00:30:29.209
That's him! He's the one
who killed Master Xuanku!

257
00:30:40.333 --> 00:30:43.707
Master. we witnessed it at the Qiao house!

258
00:30:43.708 --> 00:30:46.167
He was the one who killed
his adoptive parents!

259
00:30:46.168 --> 00:30:49.582
You cruelly killed your
parents and your teacher.

260
00:30:49.583 --> 00:30:52.499
Qiao Feng. you are not worthy
of being called a human being.

261
00:30:52.500 --> 00:30:55.542
Now. you've stolen the
temple's secret manuscript.

262
00:30:55.543 --> 00:30:59.082
Are you not bullying the Shaolin Temple?

263
00:30:59.083 --> 00:31:03.333
Dear brothers. I would never
hurt anyone in Shaolin.

264
00:31:04.793 --> 00:31:07.625
If you all believe the rumors out there.

265
00:31:11.875 --> 00:31:13.874
then I have nothing to say.

266
00:31:13.875 --> 00:31:16.959
If everyone in the world
says you are. then you are!

267
00:32:02.583 --> 00:32:04.125
- Stop!
- Don't run!

268
00:32:06.458 --> 00:32:09.083
- Stop!
- Stop!

269
00:32:10.750 --> 00:32:12.168
Catch him!

270
00:32:15.918 --> 00:32:16.918
Master.

271
00:33:01.999 --> 00:33:06.023
Shaolin Master Xuannan's Powerful
Vajra Palm injured your heart.

272
00:33:06.024 --> 00:33:09.650
My vital energy is protecting your heart
and keeping you alive.

273
00:33:09.651 --> 00:33:11.316
Otherwise. you would have died.

274
00:33:12.668 --> 00:33:13.917
Who are you?

275
00:33:13.918 --> 00:33:16.917
How dare you go to the Shaolin Temple
and steal the Tendon-Altering Sutra?

276
00:33:16.918 --> 00:33:20.042
I didn't steal it. I borrowed it.

277
00:33:20.043 --> 00:33:21.594
I'll return it after reading it.

278
00:33:23.458 --> 00:33:27.583
You noble sects are so stubborn
and love to accuse people.

279
00:33:28.958 --> 00:33:32.958
Since you think I'm a thief.
then I thank you for saving my life.

280
00:33:33.958 --> 00:33:35.293
Goodbye.

281
00:34:31.750 --> 00:34:33.168
Here. steamed buns.

282
00:34:34.583 --> 00:34:36.250
Put on some dry clothes.

283
00:34:39.109 --> 00:34:40.192
They're not stolen.

284
00:34:41.543 --> 00:34:42.543
Just borrowed.

285
00:34:50.625 --> 00:34:54.083
Your injury was all because of me.

286
00:34:58.043 --> 00:34:59.999
I'll figure something out.

287
00:35:00.000 --> 00:35:01.083
No need.

288
00:35:01.918 --> 00:35:03.375
I'll figure it out myself.

289
00:36:02.418 --> 00:36:03.680
The rain is too heavy.

290
00:36:05.793 --> 00:36:07.208
How infuriating.

291
00:36:08.793 --> 00:36:11.667
It's all that darned Qiao Feng's fault.

292
00:36:11.668 --> 00:36:14.667
He alone has caused all this chaos.

293
00:36:14.668 --> 00:36:19.082
This is such bad weather. and we still have to
run to all the sects to report the message.

294
00:36:19.083 --> 00:36:21.707
- It's crazy.
- That's right.

295
00:36:21.708 --> 00:36:24.249
I used to think that Qiao Feng was a hero.

296
00:36:24.250 --> 00:36:26.917
I didn't think he was so heartless.

297
00:36:26.918 --> 00:36:28.374
Do you know?

298
00:36:28.375 --> 00:36:33.542
Though Qiao Feng has a very poor character.
his kung fu is very powerful.

299
00:36:33.543 --> 00:36:37.624
Fortunately. the world
still has me. Bao Qianling.

300
00:36:37.625 --> 00:36:39.082
In terms of kung fu.

301
00:36:39.083 --> 00:36:42.207
I'm a match for him.

302
00:36:42.208 --> 00:36:45.708
Sometimes. I'm even a
little better than him.

303
00:36:47.083 --> 00:36:50.792
If I'm lucky today and
meet Qiao Feng on the road.

304
00:36:50.793 --> 00:36:53.918
you can watch me rip him to pieces.

305
00:36:54.668 --> 00:36:55.668
Let's go.

306
00:36:55.669 --> 00:36:56.874
Go.

307
00:36:56.875 --> 00:36:58.957
Boss. why aren't you riding a horse today?

308
00:36:58.958 --> 00:37:00.999
- I lost it.
- Lost it?

309
00:37:01.000 --> 00:37:02.457
Yes.

310
00:37:02.458 --> 00:37:03.667
- How?
- Bad luck. right?

311
00:37:03.668 --> 00:37:05.624
Just when I was getting lucky yesterday.

312
00:37:05.625 --> 00:37:07.917
I heard that Qiao Feng killed someone
at Shaolin Temple.

313
00:37:07.918 --> 00:37:11.794
This is a serious matter.
so I didn't have time to recoup my losses.

314
00:37:19.499 --> 00:37:23.082
God has opened His eyes
and sent me a horse.

315
00:37:23.083 --> 00:37:24.999
You can walk behind me.

316
00:37:25.000 --> 00:37:26.542
I'll get on my horse.

317
00:37:26.543 --> 00:37:27.874
Boss. take care.

318
00:37:27.875 --> 00:37:28.875
Yes. Boss.

319
00:37:32.293 --> 00:37:33.332
Boss!

320
00:37:33.333 --> 00:37:34.707
- Boss.
- Are you all right. Boss?

321
00:37:34.708 --> 00:37:35.938
Are you all right?

322
00:37:37.750 --> 00:37:39.958
Boss. are you going to ride the horse?

323
00:37:56.168 --> 00:37:58.208
Do you believe what they said?

324
00:38:40.793 --> 00:38:42.043
There's hope for you.

325
00:40:17.833 --> 00:40:19.043
Mr. Qiao.

326
00:40:21.168 --> 00:40:22.957
Thank you.

327
00:40:22.958 --> 00:40:26.124
I thought I was going to die this time.

328
00:40:26.125 --> 00:40:27.625
It's not that easy to die.

329
00:40:29.293 --> 00:40:31.792
You will be saved once
we find Physician Xue.

330
00:40:31.793 --> 00:40:35.707
But I heard that Physician
Xue has long disappeared.

331
00:40:35.708 --> 00:40:37.000
How will you find him?

332
00:40:37.001 --> 00:40:38.874
Don't you remember?

333
00:40:38.875 --> 00:40:40.999
I used to be the head of the Beggars' Gang.

334
00:40:41.000 --> 00:40:42.583
Of course. I have my ways.

335
00:40:43.918 --> 00:40:44.918
Then...

336
00:40:46.083 --> 00:40:49.999
do you think you can give me a bun?

337
00:40:50.000 --> 00:40:51.707
There are no more buns.

338
00:40:51.708 --> 00:40:53.266
How about some porridge?

339
00:40:56.250 --> 00:40:57.543
Does it taste good?

340
00:41:00.668 --> 00:41:04.043
Next time. let's eat buns.

341
00:41:08.555 --> 00:41:09.555
You're right.

342
00:41:10.833 --> 00:41:13.793
Why did you sneak into Shaolin Temple
to steal something?

343
00:41:14.500 --> 00:41:18.082
Actually. I'm a servant
of the Murong family.

344
00:41:18.083 --> 00:41:21.332
My master said that
if I stole the Tendon-Altering Sutra.

345
00:41:21.333 --> 00:41:23.500
he would tell me my origins.

346
00:41:24.208 --> 00:41:27.332
Then I could see my parents.

347
00:41:27.333 --> 00:41:30.875
But now. with my current injuries.

348
00:41:32.918 --> 00:41:37.168
I'm afraid that I'll
never be able to see them.

349
00:41:37.833 --> 00:41:39.250
You will see your parents.

350
00:41:40.625 --> 00:41:41.625
I promise you.

351
00:42:37.875 --> 00:42:39.315
Are you having trouble sleeping too?

352
00:42:40.708 --> 00:42:41.875
Mr. Qiao.

353
00:42:43.333 --> 00:42:44.625
Just call me Qiao.

354
00:43:00.708 --> 00:43:02.082
Qiao.

355
00:43:02.083 --> 00:43:06.083
After you send me to Physician
Xue. where will you go?

356
00:43:10.500 --> 00:43:12.293
I'm going to Yanmen Pass.

357
00:43:13.875 --> 00:43:16.125
Do you want to find your origins?

358
00:43:26.125 --> 00:43:27.583
If I were Khitan.

359
00:43:29.750 --> 00:43:32.107
would you think I'm a bad person?

360
00:43:32.108 --> 00:43:37.026
Whether you are Khitan or not.
to me. you are a good person.

361
00:43:49.293 --> 00:43:51.833
Once upon a time. there was a poor family.

362
00:43:54.250 --> 00:43:55.958
The child's father was seriously ill.

363
00:43:59.958 --> 00:44:03.000
So they took all the money they had...

364
00:44:04.500 --> 00:44:06.582
and went to find a doctor.

365
00:44:06.583 --> 00:44:09.042
But the doctor was a fraudster.

366
00:44:09.043 --> 00:44:10.875
He took the money and ignored them.

367
00:44:12.750 --> 00:44:15.624
The money was meant to
save the father's life.

368
00:44:15.625 --> 00:44:19.043
Therefore. the kid sneaked
into the fraudster's house.

369
00:44:20.208 --> 00:44:23.083
intending to get the money back.

370
00:44:23.958 --> 00:44:25.918
But the fraudster found out.

371
00:44:27.293 --> 00:44:29.668
The kid took a knife out...

372
00:44:33.675 --> 00:44:35.675
and killed the fraudster.

373
00:44:36.875 --> 00:44:38.583
With his blood-stained hands.

374
00:44:39.758 --> 00:44:41.051
he brought back the money.

375
00:44:41.875 --> 00:44:46.168
Do you think the boy brought the knife
only to get the money back?

376
00:44:49.708 --> 00:44:51.388
Or did he intend to kill someone?

377
00:44:54.168 --> 00:44:55.833
If he intended to kill someone.

378
00:44:57.667 --> 00:44:59.042
would he still be a good person?

379
00:44:59.043 --> 00:45:00.449
I would do the same thing.

380
00:45:05.793 --> 00:45:09.793
He did all that for the
sake of his loved ones.

381
00:45:18.233 --> 00:45:22.535
Then I'll tell the kid that in this world.

382
00:45:24.125 --> 00:45:25.948
there is still someone on his side.

383
00:45:30.250 --> 00:45:33.833
Then... please tell him
one more thing for me.

384
00:45:36.543 --> 00:45:37.958
Thank him for saving me.

385
00:45:45.668 --> 00:45:46.668
All right.

386
00:46:51.875 --> 00:46:56.793
Today. the world's heroes are gathered
at my Heroes' Gathering Manor!

387
00:46:57.668 --> 00:47:03.542
Working together. we can eliminate
Qiao Feng and rid the world of evil!

388
00:47:03.543 --> 00:47:04.458
Drink up!

389
00:47:04.459 --> 00:47:06.207
- Cheers!
- Cheers!

390
00:47:06.208 --> 00:47:07.292
Kill Qiao Feng!

391
00:47:07.293 --> 00:47:08.874
- Kill Qiao Feng!
- Kill Qiao Feng!

392
00:47:08.875 --> 00:47:10.124
Kill the traitor!

393
00:47:10.125 --> 00:47:11.667
- Kill the traitor!
- Kill the traitor!

394
00:47:11.668 --> 00:47:13.375
- Kill Qiao Feng!
- Kill Qiao Feng!

395
00:47:36.250 --> 00:47:37.583
Master!

396
00:47:40.958 --> 00:47:42.625
Master!

397
00:47:44.125 --> 00:47:46.167
What on earth is going on? Speak!

398
00:47:46.168 --> 00:47:47.874
Qiao...

399
00:47:47.875 --> 00:47:49.332
Qiao...

400
00:47:49.333 --> 00:47:51.250
Qiao Feng is here!

401
00:48:37.875 --> 00:48:38.875
Go!

402
00:48:44.793 --> 00:48:49.875
Qiao Feng. how dare you come to the
You brothers' Heroes' Gathering Manor!

403
00:48:56.333 --> 00:49:00.708
What a coincidence. We were discussing
how to root out scum like you.

404
00:49:02.168 --> 00:49:04.457
I've come here to see Physician Xue.

405
00:49:04.458 --> 00:49:06.500
Amitābha.

406
00:49:07.418 --> 00:49:11.582
Qiao Feng. do you know
that before Xuanku died.

407
00:49:11.583 --> 00:49:15.792
he still hoped that you could put down
the butcher's knife and repent your ways?

408
00:49:15.793 --> 00:49:21.417
Yet you conspired with a foreign woman
to steal our secret manuscript.

409
00:49:21.418 --> 00:49:24.708
You are tarnishing Shaolin's reputation!

410
00:49:31.958 --> 00:49:35.881
Qiao Feng. you have no conscience.

411
00:49:35.882 --> 00:49:37.675
You killed my husband.

412
00:49:38.418 --> 00:49:43.458
Today. even if I have to risk my life.
I want you to pay in blood!

413
00:49:47.083 --> 00:49:49.957
Heroes. I beg you all.

414
00:49:49.958 --> 00:49:53.292
You must help me get justice.

415
00:49:53.293 --> 00:49:54.957
Mrs. Ma.

416
00:49:54.958 --> 00:50:00.833
we have yet to determine
whether Qiao Feng killed Vice Master Ma.

417
00:50:01.543 --> 00:50:04.499
Isn't your conduct thus unbecoming?

418
00:50:04.500 --> 00:50:07.042
We're here today to eliminate the traitor.

419
00:50:07.043 --> 00:50:10.417
But you seem to be
defending Qiao Feng instead.

420
00:50:10.418 --> 00:50:12.167
I would like to ask

421
00:50:12.168 --> 00:50:15.999
whether the Beggars' Gang is trying
to protect this Khitan dog traitor!

422
00:50:16.000 --> 00:50:19.333
This is the Beggars' Gang's business!
Who dares to question us?

423
00:50:22.293 --> 00:50:23.668
That's enough!

424
00:50:25.168 --> 00:50:27.707
Why are you arguing among yourselves?

425
00:50:27.708 --> 00:50:29.833
Outsiders would think of us as a joke.

426
00:50:35.293 --> 00:50:37.458
Physician Xue. I beg for your help.

427
00:50:39.458 --> 00:50:42.418
Ms. Azhu is seriously
injured because of me.

428
00:50:44.667 --> 00:50:49.543
I came here today because you are the
only one in the world who can save her.

429
00:50:50.341 --> 00:50:52.207
If you help me today.

430
00:50:52.208 --> 00:50:55.168
I. Qiao Feng. will repay you one day.

431
00:50:59.208 --> 00:51:01.707
She was injured by the Powerful Vajra Palm.

432
00:51:01.708 --> 00:51:04.207
If you hadn't kept her alive
using your inner strength.

433
00:51:04.208 --> 00:51:06.418
she wouldn't have survived this long.

434
00:51:07.793 --> 00:51:13.668
All healers ought to have
healing hands and kind hearts.

435
00:51:15.168 --> 00:51:19.958
I won't turn away anyone
who seeks medical help.

436
00:51:20.874 --> 00:51:23.499
except for anyone brought by you.

437
00:51:23.500 --> 00:51:25.168
I won't save any of them.

438
00:51:26.500 --> 00:51:28.457
You are a Khitan.

439
00:51:28.458 --> 00:51:30.457
You learned the kung
fu of the Central Plain

440
00:51:30.458 --> 00:51:32.792
and used it to kill the
people of the Central Plain.

441
00:51:32.793 --> 00:51:34.499
That is a sin!

442
00:51:34.500 --> 00:51:36.417
How can I tolerate your behavior?

443
00:51:36.418 --> 00:51:38.082
Physician Xue is right!

444
00:51:38.083 --> 00:51:40.292
Kill this Khitan traitor!

445
00:51:40.293 --> 00:51:42.917
- Kill him!
- Kill him!

446
00:51:42.918 --> 00:51:45.668
All who are present are heroes!

447
00:51:46.668 --> 00:51:48.418
You ought to know right from wrong.

448
00:51:50.418 --> 00:51:52.332
It's me that you want to kill.

449
00:51:52.333 --> 00:51:54.332
This lady has nothing to do with it.

450
00:51:54.333 --> 00:51:58.158
Are you going to stand back
and watch this innocent woman die?

451
00:51:58.159 --> 00:52:01.707
This goes against your intention
to practice medicine to help the world.

452
00:52:01.708 --> 00:52:05.749
Qiao Feng. since you want
to save this lady so badly.

453
00:52:05.750 --> 00:52:12.500
if we ask you today to give your
life for hers. will you say yes?

454
00:52:13.168 --> 00:52:19.249
It would be my pleasure
to save a close friend with my life!

455
00:52:19.250 --> 00:52:24.499
However. we shall see
whether you are capable of taking my life.

456
00:52:24.500 --> 00:52:28.668
Leave your life behind and
I'll save her life for you.

457
00:52:29.918 --> 00:52:30.918
Thank you.

458
00:52:39.583 --> 00:52:40.668
Qiao.

459
00:52:41.500 --> 00:52:43.083
I don't want treatment anymore.

460
00:52:57.083 --> 00:52:59.625
There are many of my former brothers here.

461
00:53:07.708 --> 00:53:09.375
Today. we are enemies. not friends.

462
00:53:12.668 --> 00:53:15.043
The world's heroes say I'm a Khitan.

463
00:53:17.543 --> 00:53:19.043
They say I killed my beloved teacher.

464
00:53:20.793 --> 00:53:23.124
my parents.

465
00:53:23.125 --> 00:53:24.511
and my old friends.

466
00:53:25.933 --> 00:53:29.293
If you wish to condemn
me. no pretext is needed.

467
00:53:42.458 --> 00:53:44.832
Take this as a wine of severance.

468
00:53:44.833 --> 00:53:47.082
After drinking it.

469
00:53:47.083 --> 00:53:49.374
we shall write off all past grudges.

470
00:53:49.375 --> 00:53:53.249
If you kill me. it will not be ingratitude.

471
00:53:53.250 --> 00:53:56.543
If I kill you. it will not be an injustice.

472
00:53:57.458 --> 00:53:58.833
Heroes of the world.

473
00:54:00.875 --> 00:54:02.250
bear witness to this.

474
00:54:07.875 --> 00:54:11.250
Any of you who wish to take my life.
step up and drink with me.

475
00:54:18.625 --> 00:54:19.625
I'll drink.

476
00:54:28.208 --> 00:54:29.208
Qiao Feng.

477
00:54:29.917 --> 00:54:33.208
everyone in this world
thinks you're a hero.

478
00:54:33.917 --> 00:54:38.833
I never thought that you would
sacrifice your life to save a woman.

479
00:54:41.875 --> 00:54:46.043
My late husband died at your hand.
You and I are no longer friends.

480
00:54:51.833 --> 00:54:57.043
I will drink this bowl of
wine on behalf of my husband.

481
00:55:18.708 --> 00:55:22.501
The Fourfold Assembly of Buddhism
must abide by the precept of alcohol.

482
00:55:23.293 --> 00:55:26.333
Today. I'll use tea in place of wine.

483
00:55:28.601 --> 00:55:29.644
Qiao Feng.

484
00:55:30.333 --> 00:55:33.333
I trained you in Shaolin
since you were a child.

485
00:55:34.333 --> 00:55:38.043
I didn't expect that our fate
would come to this today.

486
00:55:43.708 --> 00:55:45.457
So be it.

487
00:55:45.458 --> 00:55:47.875
Buddha will not accept
those who aren't destined.

488
00:55:49.250 --> 00:55:52.624
Sow this cause and reap the fruits.

489
00:55:52.625 --> 00:55:54.500
Everything stems from the heart. Master.

490
00:55:57.758 --> 00:55:59.254
After drinking this bowl of wine.

491
00:56:00.958 --> 00:56:04.249
I'll no longer hold back with you.

492
00:56:04.250 --> 00:56:05.333
Very well.

493
00:56:17.668 --> 00:56:19.457
- Amitābha.
- Amitābha.

494
00:56:19.458 --> 00:56:24.042
Qiao Feng. our brothers almost died west of
the pass to a group of Western Xia soldiers.

495
00:56:24.043 --> 00:56:27.582
Fortunately. you came to our rescue.
We are indeed indebted to you.

496
00:56:27.583 --> 00:56:31.417
But in the face of justice.
personal favors are not worth mentioning.

497
00:56:31.418 --> 00:56:34.917
I. Xiang Wanghai. admire
very few people in my life.

498
00:56:34.918 --> 00:56:36.207
I. Qi Liu. as well.

499
00:56:36.208 --> 00:56:37.250
- Bottoms up!
- Bottoms up!

500
00:56:45.500 --> 00:56:48.417
The Beggars' Gang's current system
for reward and punishment is clear-cut.

501
00:56:48.418 --> 00:56:50.250
You established this standard.

502
00:56:51.458 --> 00:56:52.750
I drink to you.

503
00:56:53.918 --> 00:56:56.792
The gang is strengthened
and prepared for war.

504
00:56:56.793 --> 00:56:59.042
You deserve the credit for that.

505
00:56:59.043 --> 00:57:04.250
I toast to you on behalf
of the Beggars' Gang.

506
00:57:04.918 --> 00:57:09.792
The gang has set up a web of
spies thanks to your help.

507
00:57:09.793 --> 00:57:10.793
To you!

508
00:57:12.500 --> 00:57:15.207
In many instances when
assassinating foreign enemies.

509
00:57:15.208 --> 00:57:17.624
without your intervention.

510
00:57:17.625 --> 00:57:20.207
our brothers would have
been killed long ago.

511
00:57:20.208 --> 00:57:21.293
To you.

512
00:57:26.208 --> 00:57:30.167
We have fought and killed enemies together
in the battlefield.

513
00:57:30.168 --> 00:57:33.624
We were good brothers who
braved death together.

514
00:57:33.625 --> 00:57:37.168
Unfortunately. one of us must die today.

515
00:57:38.543 --> 00:57:39.708
To you!

516
00:57:41.333 --> 00:57:45.333
To be able to go through battles
with all of you so many times...

517
00:57:47.708 --> 00:57:49.458
was my good fortune.

518
00:57:52.750 --> 00:57:54.043
After drinking this wine.

519
00:57:56.340 --> 00:57:58.999
our relationship will end here.

520
00:57:59.000 --> 00:58:00.333
In the next life.

521
00:58:02.875 --> 00:58:05.708
I hope we can still be good brothers.

522
00:58:14.000 --> 00:58:15.082
Please!

523
00:58:15.083 --> 00:58:16.293
- Please!
- Please!

524
00:58:42.168 --> 00:58:43.249
Boss.

525
00:58:43.250 --> 00:58:47.082
Didn't you always want to
rip Qiao Feng to pieces?

526
00:58:47.083 --> 00:58:48.999
Now is the chance.

527
00:58:49.000 --> 00:58:51.501
Boss. this is a good opportunity. Go ahead.

528
00:58:57.250 --> 00:58:58.625
- Go.
- All right.

529
00:59:10.793 --> 00:59:12.167
Qiao Feng.

530
00:59:12.168 --> 00:59:14.207
I'll have a drink with you too.

531
00:59:14.208 --> 00:59:16.583
I'm drinking with all the heroes.

532
00:59:17.625 --> 00:59:20.458
Who are you? You are not worthy!

533
00:59:21.749 --> 00:59:25.875
Let me tell you. I'm drinking this
wine with you out of respect for you.

534
00:59:26.792 --> 00:59:34.624
This man is the Khitan traitor who murdered
his parents and betrayed his master!

535
00:59:34.625 --> 00:59:37.832
You don't deserve to
drink this wine with me.

536
00:59:37.833 --> 00:59:40.168
I'll drink it by myself. I'll drink alone.

537
00:59:47.043 --> 00:59:48.624
Khitan traitor!

538
00:59:48.625 --> 00:59:50.043
I'll kill you!

539
00:59:50.044 --> 00:59:51.669
I'll take your damned life!

540
01:00:02.874 --> 01:00:05.624
Come at me together!
What are you waiting for?

541
01:00:05.625 --> 01:00:07.793
Beggars' Gang. go!

542
01:00:28.043 --> 01:00:29.043
Flip it over!

543
01:01:41.043 --> 01:01:42.625
I'm going to kill you. Khitan dog!

544
01:02:15.375 --> 01:02:16.708
- Master!
- Master!

545
01:02:36.418 --> 01:02:37.418
Qiao.

546
01:03:04.833 --> 01:03:08.125
Qiao Feng. you must die
for the sake of the martial arts world!

547
01:03:31.625 --> 01:03:33.418
The Proud Dragon Repents!

548
01:03:57.208 --> 01:03:59.042
Disciples of Heroes' Gathering Manor.

549
01:03:59.043 --> 01:04:00.043
Take formation!

550
01:04:37.583 --> 01:04:38.799
Qiao Feng!

551
01:04:38.800 --> 01:04:41.465
She shall pay for what you have done!

552
01:05:42.168 --> 01:05:43.168
Azhu.

553
01:06:12.168 --> 01:06:13.418
Go to hell!

554
01:06:16.625 --> 01:06:17.625
Qiao!

555
01:06:27.333 --> 01:06:28.500
Qiao.

556
01:06:34.500 --> 01:06:35.500
Qiao.

557
01:06:36.668 --> 01:06:39.167
You knew they would kill you.

558
01:06:39.168 --> 01:06:41.293
Why did you still come here?

559
01:06:43.543 --> 01:06:45.043
I promised to save you.

560
01:06:48.668 --> 01:06:49.875
Is it worth it?

561
01:06:52.958 --> 01:06:54.000
It's worth it.

562
01:06:55.625 --> 01:06:56.875
In this world.

563
01:06:59.707 --> 01:07:03.043
you are the only one who still trusts me.

564
01:07:35.543 --> 01:07:36.918
Eighteen Subduing Dragon Palms?

565
01:07:44.043 --> 01:07:45.707
Qiao.

566
01:07:45.708 --> 01:07:48.465
Qiao. run. Don't worry about me.

567
01:07:48.466 --> 01:07:49.633
Qiao.

568
01:08:08.875 --> 01:08:12.332
To be a real man means to be
a man among men while alive

569
01:08:12.333 --> 01:08:14.707
and a ghost among ghosts when dead!

570
01:08:14.708 --> 01:08:15.833
Since death awaits.

571
01:08:17.458 --> 01:08:19.000
I'll die with you!

572
01:08:19.750 --> 01:08:20.750
Come on!

573
01:08:22.000 --> 01:08:24.917
I've stabbed his Qi Hui acupoint.

574
01:08:24.918 --> 01:08:26.457
He can't use his power anymore.

575
01:08:26.458 --> 01:08:28.542
Now is not the time for morality!

576
01:08:28.543 --> 01:08:29.875
Kill him quickly!

577
01:08:32.543 --> 01:08:33.707
Kill him!

578
01:08:33.708 --> 01:08:36.083
And kill the girl too!

579
01:10:31.333 --> 01:10:34.043
God's will cannot be disobeyed.

580
01:10:38.125 --> 01:10:42.043
Without Qiao Feng. who else
can come to your rescue?

581
01:10:46.543 --> 01:10:47.958
Why kill her?

582
01:10:49.875 --> 01:10:52.542
Qiao Feng would give up his life for her.

583
01:10:52.543 --> 01:10:54.417
Let me heal her.

584
01:10:54.418 --> 01:10:56.333
Qiao Feng will surely return.

585
01:11:32.958 --> 01:11:35.543
[Xing]

586
01:11:45.375 --> 01:11:47.500
[Yan]

587
01:11:50.168 --> 01:11:51.250
Father.

588
01:11:52.793 --> 01:11:53.833
I have...

589
01:11:55.083 --> 01:12:01.707
followed your last wish to conceal my light
and endure hardships.

590
01:12:01.708 --> 01:12:03.582
This day has finally come.

591
01:12:03.583 --> 01:12:07.499
Today. the Song dynasty is
already full of devastation.

592
01:12:07.500 --> 01:12:11.125
Once I defeat Qiao Feng.

593
01:12:12.250 --> 01:12:17.708
it will be time for our Great Yan
to mete out great justice!

594
01:12:30.918 --> 01:12:33.125
Great Yan's sword...

595
01:12:34.875 --> 01:12:36.918
has been covered in dust for a long time.

596
01:12:39.250 --> 01:12:40.958
The day it is unsheathed.

597
01:12:41.902 --> 01:12:43.609
it will be...

598
01:12:45.208 --> 01:12:48.083
invincible!

599
01:13:00.125 --> 01:13:01.832
I have recovered.

600
01:13:01.833 --> 01:13:03.792
Let me go.

601
01:13:03.793 --> 01:13:05.832
I saved your life.

602
01:13:05.833 --> 01:13:09.583
Only when I want you to go can you leave.

603
01:13:10.543 --> 01:13:12.417
Qiao must still be alive.

604
01:13:12.418 --> 01:13:14.418
He will definitely come back to save me.

605
01:13:15.856 --> 01:13:19.417
By then. I'm afraid you'll
be the first to leave.

606
01:13:19.418 --> 01:13:22.499
I've been helping the world for years.

607
01:13:22.500 --> 01:13:25.582
How many people have I saved?

608
01:13:25.583 --> 01:13:27.707
What have I gained?

609
01:13:27.708 --> 01:13:30.124
They are all hypocrites and villains!

610
01:13:30.125 --> 01:13:32.499
Qiao Feng is a villain.

611
01:13:32.500 --> 01:13:35.417
Everyone in the world wants to kill him.

612
01:13:35.418 --> 01:13:37.792
But in their hearts. they still fear him.

613
01:13:37.793 --> 01:13:39.042
Why?

614
01:13:39.043 --> 01:13:41.543
It's because he's
different from all of you.

615
01:14:08.083 --> 01:14:09.625
I knew you were tough.

616
01:14:10.458 --> 01:14:11.778
You would not die so easily.

617
01:14:12.418 --> 01:14:15.542
There is food on the table. Help yourself.

618
01:14:15.543 --> 01:14:17.582
Thank you for saving my life.

619
01:14:17.583 --> 01:14:22.417
If it weren't for your deep internal strength.
I couldn't have saved you even if I wanted to.

620
01:14:22.418 --> 01:14:25.707
Do you know what destiny is?

621
01:14:25.708 --> 01:14:28.042
What can you tell me?

622
01:14:28.043 --> 01:14:34.249
Grudges and strife are the destiny of the
country and the destiny of man even more so.

623
01:14:34.250 --> 01:14:37.624
In this world. love and revenge
are difficult to overcome.

624
01:14:37.625 --> 01:14:43.226
All causes and effects in the world
cannot escape love and injustice.

625
01:14:43.227 --> 01:14:46.853
No one is an exception. Those who
have feelings are all caught in them.

626
01:14:46.854 --> 01:14:49.833
In fact. life and death
are the same as nirvana.

627
01:14:51.583 --> 01:14:54.917
Emotion and non-emotion are no different.
Everything comes from the heart. sir.

628
01:14:54.918 --> 01:14:59.292
You are a Khitan. but you gave up your life
for a Song woman.

629
01:14:59.293 --> 01:15:00.583
You need to know.

630
01:15:01.583 --> 01:15:05.457
The hatred between you and
the Song is irreconcilable.

631
01:15:05.458 --> 01:15:10.500
If you die like this.
how can you face your real parents?

632
01:15:11.543 --> 01:15:14.083
Whether it's the Khitan or the Song.

633
01:15:15.583 --> 01:15:17.707
I believe that my biological parents

634
01:15:17.708 --> 01:15:20.333
were not the kind of people
who turn away from love and justice.

635
01:15:23.668 --> 01:15:28.403
Your father. Xiao Yuanshan. was indeed
not a heartless and unrighteous man.

636
01:15:29.250 --> 01:15:31.299
Do you know about my real parents?

637
01:15:31.300 --> 01:15:32.715
Who are you?

638
01:15:35.125 --> 01:15:37.042
It doesn't matter who I am.

639
01:15:37.043 --> 01:15:41.415
The most important thing
is that you know who you are.

640
01:15:57.208 --> 01:15:58.499
Somebody!

641
01:15:58.500 --> 01:16:00.249
Somebody. open the door!

642
01:16:00.250 --> 01:16:01.418
Hurry up!

643
01:16:02.168 --> 01:16:03.999
That darned girl hurt me!

644
01:16:04.000 --> 01:16:06.043
She's gone! Go after her!

645
01:16:08.333 --> 01:16:10.874
All of you. go after her!

646
01:16:10.875 --> 01:16:11.875
Go!

647
01:16:25.958 --> 01:16:27.625
What is all the ruckus?

648
01:16:44.833 --> 01:16:46.708
This is for Qiao.

649
01:16:52.833 --> 01:16:55.917
This is a minor injury. I'll heal myself.

650
01:16:55.918 --> 01:16:57.707
When I get better.

651
01:16:57.708 --> 01:17:01.293
I'll gather all martial artists
and destroy you and that Khitan dog!

652
01:17:04.708 --> 01:17:07.457
No!

653
01:17:07.458 --> 01:17:09.542
No! My medical clinic!

654
01:17:09.543 --> 01:17:11.582
My medicine! My medical clinic!

655
01:17:11.583 --> 01:17:13.667
My medicine! My medical clinic!

656
01:17:13.668 --> 01:17:14.958
It's gone!

657
01:17:16.583 --> 01:17:17.583
Sir!

658
01:17:19.750 --> 01:17:20.708
- Sir.
- Sir.

659
01:17:20.709 --> 01:17:21.833
Azhu is not dead.

660
01:17:28.333 --> 01:17:29.958
That means...

661
01:17:31.793 --> 01:17:34.043
Qiao Feng will definitely appear.

662
01:18:03.708 --> 01:18:07.668
Indeed. "Murong in the south.
Qiao Feng in the north."

663
01:18:09.418 --> 01:18:11.043
You are Murong Fu of Gusu.

664
01:18:12.293 --> 01:18:15.417
Why is a man from a prestigious family
attacking from behind?

665
01:18:15.418 --> 01:18:16.792
What do you mean by this?

666
01:18:16.793 --> 01:18:17.793
Qiao Feng.

667
01:18:18.750 --> 01:18:20.249
your Song dynasty

668
01:18:20.250 --> 01:18:23.457
suffers from internal and external troubles
and values literature over kung fu.

669
01:18:23.458 --> 01:18:25.917
The Songs have turned their backs on you.

670
01:18:25.918 --> 01:18:31.792
Why don't you and I join hands
and work together to conquer the world?

671
01:18:31.793 --> 01:18:33.583
Although I'm a man of the world.

672
01:18:34.708 --> 01:18:38.875
what is right and what is wrong
are very clear to me.

673
01:18:40.168 --> 01:18:43.707
You and I walk different paths.
We cannot work together.

674
01:18:43.708 --> 01:18:47.918
With how the Songs have treated you.
don't you hate them at all?

675
01:18:48.668 --> 01:18:52.832
What I hate are those who
stir up unnecessary strife.

676
01:18:52.833 --> 01:18:57.917
Strife in the world is
either for fame or benefits.

677
01:18:57.918 --> 01:18:59.625
There is no such thing as unnecessary.

678
01:19:03.465 --> 01:19:07.007
Did you come here to look for Azhu?

679
01:19:29.043 --> 01:19:30.208
Hurry up!

680
01:19:32.250 --> 01:19:33.250
Hurry up!

681
01:19:34.083 --> 01:19:35.833
- Don't play tricks!
- Keep walking!

682
01:19:37.292 --> 01:19:38.624
Khitan dogs.

683
01:19:38.625 --> 01:19:39.793
Hurry up!

684
01:19:40.543 --> 01:19:42.125
Grandpa.

685
01:19:42.126 --> 01:19:43.626
I can't walk anymore.

686
01:19:44.333 --> 01:19:45.958
I want to drink water.

687
01:19:50.043 --> 01:19:51.124
Hurry up!

688
01:19:51.125 --> 01:19:52.832
Sir.

689
01:19:52.833 --> 01:19:55.249
We've been walking for two days.

690
01:19:55.250 --> 01:19:58.708
Have mercy on us. Give us some water.

691
01:20:02.869 --> 01:20:04.324
- Stop!
- Stop!

692
01:20:06.293 --> 01:20:07.999
- Do you want some water?
- Yes.

693
01:20:08.000 --> 01:20:09.203
Do you want a drink?

694
01:20:09.204 --> 01:20:11.122
- Come on.
- Thank you.

695
01:20:14.543 --> 01:20:16.457
Do you want to drink water?

696
01:20:16.458 --> 01:20:17.958
You Khitan dogs!

697
01:20:18.625 --> 01:20:20.749
Aren't you born strong and tough?

698
01:20:20.750 --> 01:20:22.793
Do you need water? Really?

699
01:20:23.543 --> 01:20:25.081
Do you still want to drink?

700
01:20:37.293 --> 01:20:40.043
Did you think the Song people would lose
when you battled us?

701
01:20:40.708 --> 01:20:43.167
I'll beat you now. Khitan dogs!

702
01:20:43.168 --> 01:20:45.874
- Do you dare to battle us?
- Stop beating my grandpa!

703
01:20:45.875 --> 01:20:47.293
Khitan dog!

704
01:20:48.458 --> 01:20:49.500
Stop!

705
01:20:50.207 --> 01:20:51.874
Don't!

706
01:20:51.875 --> 01:20:52.995
Go to hell!

707
01:21:32.833 --> 01:21:34.125
Go home.

708
01:21:41.083 --> 01:21:43.874
If I were Khitan. would
you think I'm a bad person?

709
01:21:43.875 --> 01:21:47.957
Whether you are Khitan or not.
to me. you are a good person.

710
01:21:47.958 --> 01:21:49.207
You are a Khitan.

711
01:21:49.208 --> 01:21:51.742
You learned the kung fu of the Central Plain
to kill the people of the Central Plain.

712
01:21:51.743 --> 01:21:53.586
You really are a Khitan bastard!
You're worse than animals!

713
01:21:53.587 --> 01:21:55.542
I'll never harm a single Song life.

714
01:21:55.543 --> 01:21:58.332
I'll never harm a single
Song life as long as I live.

715
01:21:58.333 --> 01:22:01.250
Would you think I'm a bad person?

716
01:23:29.168 --> 01:23:30.168
Qiao!

717
01:23:49.543 --> 01:23:50.750
I thought...

718
01:23:51.875 --> 01:23:55.250
I thought I would never see you again.

719
01:23:56.042 --> 01:23:59.624
After I recovered.
I looked for you everywhere.

720
01:23:59.625 --> 01:24:01.874
I've been waiting for
you here for five days.

721
01:24:01.875 --> 01:24:04.999
I was thinking I would
keep waiting for you here.

722
01:24:05.000 --> 01:24:08.582
I would wait for you because
I knew you would be all right.

723
01:24:08.583 --> 01:24:10.250
You were going to be all right.

724
01:24:19.083 --> 01:24:21.292
From today onward.

725
01:24:21.293 --> 01:24:23.875
I'll no longer be ashamed of the Khitan.

726
01:24:24.708 --> 01:24:26.833
Nor will I be proud of the Song.

727
01:24:28.875 --> 01:24:32.443
When I find out my origins
and you reunite with your parents.

728
01:24:33.500 --> 01:24:35.180
I'll withdraw from the martial arts world.

729
01:24:36.958 --> 01:24:39.750
We shall leave the state
and herd cattle and sheep.

730
01:24:42.543 --> 01:24:44.423
Worldly affairs shall no
longer be our concern.

731
01:24:46.543 --> 01:24:47.543
Azhu.

732
01:24:48.833 --> 01:24:50.043
come with me.

733
01:24:53.958 --> 01:24:56.207
Whether you are Khitan or not.

734
01:24:56.208 --> 01:25:00.249
I had already made up my mind when we
were separated at Heroes' Gathering Manor.

735
01:25:00.250 --> 01:25:01.458
I'll follow you...

736
01:25:02.708 --> 01:25:04.208
for the rest of my life.

737
01:25:31.250 --> 01:25:32.582
Mrs. Ma.

738
01:25:32.583 --> 01:25:35.499
Physician Xue was burned to death.

739
01:25:35.500 --> 01:25:38.793
Perhaps Qiao Feng went to save that bitch.

740
01:25:40.083 --> 01:25:42.332
Is Qiao Feng not dead yet?

741
01:25:42.333 --> 01:25:48.542
If Qiao Feng is really not dead and finds
out that Ma Dayuan died at our hands.

742
01:25:48.543 --> 01:25:50.874
he will definitely come back for revenge.

743
01:25:50.875 --> 01:25:54.083
But we were just following the command
of the leading brother.

744
01:25:54.793 --> 01:25:58.668
How about we go see the leading brother?

745
01:26:00.875 --> 01:26:04.544
But his whereabouts are unpredictable
and he remains elusive.

746
01:26:12.168 --> 01:26:17.042
The leading brother. Duan
Zhengchun. is not in Dali.

747
01:26:17.043 --> 01:26:18.208
He is already here.

748
01:26:18.918 --> 01:26:20.208
He is at Mirror Lake.

749
01:27:18.832 --> 01:27:21.874
Xiaokang. it is done.

750
01:27:21.875 --> 01:27:23.250
You are so smart.

751
01:27:24.043 --> 01:27:28.958
This time. Duan Zhengchun will surely die.

752
01:27:30.279 --> 01:27:31.333
However.

753
01:27:32.708 --> 01:27:35.168
are you really willing to let him die?

754
01:27:38.792 --> 01:27:44.624
For those men who have wronged me.
death is already clemency.

755
01:27:48.241 --> 01:27:52.624
I. Bai Shijing. will never betray you.

756
01:27:52.625 --> 01:27:53.958
Are you afraid?

757
01:27:56.833 --> 01:27:58.293
Don't be afraid.

758
01:28:01.458 --> 01:28:02.668
Even if you die.

759
01:28:04.874 --> 01:28:09.958
I'll let you die comfortably.

760
01:29:05.543 --> 01:29:06.881
Why won't you let me kill him?

761
01:29:08.543 --> 01:29:09.543
Your Highness.

762
01:29:21.625 --> 01:29:22.625
Azi!

763
01:29:23.583 --> 01:29:25.207
Azi.

764
01:29:25.208 --> 01:29:26.918
She is your daughter!

765
01:29:28.833 --> 01:29:32.207
You put this golden lock
on her yourself back then.

766
01:29:32.208 --> 01:29:35.332
It's engraved with part of my name. "Zhu."
Don't you recognize it?

767
01:29:35.333 --> 01:29:36.701
Is she my daughter?

768
01:29:37.834 --> 01:29:39.124
I came back because I want...

769
01:29:39.125 --> 01:29:40.365
I don't have a father.

770
01:29:42.417 --> 01:29:45.917
Since I was a child. I have been on my own.

771
01:29:45.918 --> 01:29:49.150
Since you had abandoned me so cruelly.
don't expect me to acknowledge you.

772
01:29:53.301 --> 01:29:54.341
Take it back.

773
01:29:58.083 --> 01:29:59.458
You don't deserve to be my father!

774
01:30:04.583 --> 01:30:05.625
[Zhu]

775
01:30:29.250 --> 01:30:31.042
Thank you for saving me.

776
01:30:31.043 --> 01:30:32.309
No need to say thank you.

777
01:30:32.310 --> 01:30:36.208
I just can't stand
seeing people stab others in the back.

778
01:30:37.457 --> 01:30:41.208
You are heroic and chivalrous.
What have you come to my Mirror Lake for?

779
01:30:46.208 --> 01:30:47.707
Are you Duan Zhengchun?

780
01:30:47.708 --> 01:30:48.793
I am.

781
01:30:51.250 --> 01:30:52.293
I'm Qiao Feng.

782
01:30:53.750 --> 01:30:55.749
I was just coming to find you.

783
01:30:55.750 --> 01:30:57.332
Are you Qiao Feng. the great hero?

784
01:30:57.333 --> 01:31:00.042
I know that my son Duan Yu
and you are sworn brothers.

785
01:31:00.043 --> 01:31:01.458
I have always wanted to meet you.

786
01:31:02.833 --> 01:31:04.582
My son is naughty.

787
01:31:04.583 --> 01:31:08.167
I locked him up in the temple
in front of the mountain to meditate.

788
01:31:08.168 --> 01:31:09.625
God must have willed this day.

789
01:31:10.793 --> 01:31:11.793
Yes.

790
01:31:12.625 --> 01:31:14.332
It is the will of God.

791
01:31:14.333 --> 01:31:18.793
In that case. I shall invite you two
to the Mirror Lake courtyard tonight.

792
01:31:22.168 --> 01:31:24.417
I'll come to see you tonight.

793
01:31:24.418 --> 01:31:25.418
Good.

794
01:31:32.250 --> 01:31:34.667
Your Highness. you haven't
come for a long time.

795
01:31:34.668 --> 01:31:37.293
What are you here for this time?

796
01:31:39.333 --> 01:31:40.543
I wanted to see you.

797
01:31:43.333 --> 01:31:47.125
Although I wasn't here.
you were always on my mind.

798
01:31:51.875 --> 01:31:55.750
Do you really think I don't know
how many women you have out there?

799
01:31:57.250 --> 01:31:59.168
How can you believe the rumors?

800
01:32:00.668 --> 01:32:02.582
Take Qiao Feng for example.

801
01:32:02.583 --> 01:32:05.624
Everyone in the world says he's a villain.

802
01:32:05.625 --> 01:32:09.582
But I believe he is loyal and righteous
and would not do such things.

803
01:32:09.583 --> 01:32:11.417
Am I not just like him?

804
01:32:11.418 --> 01:32:13.500
I never care what other people say.

805
01:32:15.965 --> 01:32:22.125
I just hope that the people around me
can understand me completely.

806
01:32:23.043 --> 01:32:26.832
Just give me a chance to take
you and Azi back to Dali.

807
01:32:26.833 --> 01:32:29.667
Let me be a good father and husband.

808
01:32:29.668 --> 01:32:30.982
Let's have a family reunion.

809
01:32:32.750 --> 01:32:34.125
Family reunion?

810
01:32:37.543 --> 01:32:40.124
Don't you know that Azi has a sister?

811
01:32:40.125 --> 01:32:42.167
A sister? Where is she?

812
01:32:42.168 --> 01:32:43.668
I gave her to someone else.

813
01:32:45.045 --> 01:32:47.792
- Why did you do that?
- Why did I do that?

814
01:32:47.793 --> 01:32:51.874
Your Highness. you have so many concubines.
women. and children.

815
01:32:51.875 --> 01:32:54.292
Would you care about this daughter?

816
01:32:54.293 --> 01:32:57.457
I deliberately gave her to someone else
so that she would hate you for life.

817
01:32:57.458 --> 01:32:59.918
Even if she kills you herself.
I would think you deserve it!

818
01:33:02.875 --> 01:33:03.875
Go away!

819
01:33:17.918 --> 01:33:18.999
Azi.

820
01:33:19.000 --> 01:33:21.042
You aren't going to kill
your father. are you?

821
01:33:21.043 --> 01:33:24.542
You just said that if I kill him.
he would deserve it anyway!

822
01:33:24.543 --> 01:33:26.082
He doesn't deserve to die right now.

823
01:33:26.083 --> 01:33:27.999
Don't scold my daughter for my sake.

824
01:33:28.000 --> 01:33:28.918
Shut up!

825
01:33:28.919 --> 01:33:31.958
Azi. it is all my fault. Don't fight.

826
01:33:45.875 --> 01:33:47.583
What are you doing sneaking around?

827
01:33:50.293 --> 01:33:52.168
Are you a friend of Mr. Qiao?

828
01:33:57.875 --> 01:34:02.125
I came here to return
what you dropped earlier.

829
01:34:06.875 --> 01:34:07.875
Thank you.

830
01:34:11.833 --> 01:34:13.043
Is there anything else?

831
01:34:27.215 --> 01:34:30.708
Your daughter loves you.

832
01:34:32.875 --> 01:34:33.918
I know.

833
01:34:34.875 --> 01:34:38.293
As a father. I also love
my daughter very much.

834
01:35:11.918 --> 01:35:12.918
Azhu.

835
01:35:17.750 --> 01:35:19.418
Drink with me tonight.

836
01:35:38.125 --> 01:35:39.125
Qiao.

837
01:35:40.668 --> 01:35:43.750
Why didn't you make your move today?

838
01:35:44.833 --> 01:35:46.458
There is one more person I must see.

839
01:35:52.083 --> 01:35:53.333
Qiao.

840
01:35:55.750 --> 01:35:57.168
Meeting you...

841
01:35:58.543 --> 01:36:00.793
and experiencing so many things with you...

842
01:36:03.543 --> 01:36:08.250
were the best things
that happened in my life.

843
01:36:13.023 --> 01:36:15.958
So no matter what happens.

844
01:36:17.042 --> 01:36:20.007
I hope you can resolve
the burdens on your heart.

845
01:36:23.875 --> 01:36:27.208
After tonight. I'll take
you across the border.

846
01:36:28.625 --> 01:36:29.625
All right?

847
01:36:33.707 --> 01:36:35.207
All right.

848
01:36:35.208 --> 01:36:37.416
Once we are there.

849
01:36:37.417 --> 01:36:40.249
I'll herd cattle and you can herd sheep.

850
01:36:41.543 --> 01:36:45.418
We can live the rest of
our lives without care.

851
01:36:54.333 --> 01:36:58.250
[The Lotus Sutra]

852
01:37:15.293 --> 01:37:16.293
Qiao?

853
01:37:17.676 --> 01:37:18.933
Why are you here?

854
01:37:26.800 --> 01:37:27.882
Duan Yu.

855
01:37:28.708 --> 01:37:31.875
your father. Duan Zhengchun.
is the one who killed my parents.

856
01:37:32.918 --> 01:37:35.875
I'm going to end it with him tonight.

857
01:37:37.708 --> 01:37:39.792
I consider you a friend.

858
01:37:39.793 --> 01:37:43.168
By all rights. I had to tell you in person.

859
01:37:45.043 --> 01:37:48.278
After tonight. if you wish
to avenge your father.

860
01:37:49.500 --> 01:37:50.708
I won't run away.

861
01:37:58.875 --> 01:38:00.875
Sir!

862
01:38:01.957 --> 01:38:03.207
I'm Xuzhu.

863
01:38:03.208 --> 01:38:04.874
I see your hostile energy.

864
01:38:04.875 --> 01:38:08.958
I would like to advise you that a single
thought can turn you into a Buddha or a devil!

865
01:38:27.833 --> 01:38:28.833
Mr. Qiao.

866
01:38:35.043 --> 01:38:38.249
Duan Zhengchun. where is Azhu?

867
01:38:38.250 --> 01:38:39.418
She's fine.

868
01:38:40.875 --> 01:38:43.124
I know what you came here for today.

869
01:38:43.125 --> 01:38:44.957
That's right.

870
01:38:44.958 --> 01:38:48.042
The bloodshed at Yanmen Pass 30 years ago.

871
01:38:48.043 --> 01:38:51.293
Admit it or not. you
were the leading brother.

872
01:38:52.208 --> 01:38:53.918
It was my fault back then.

873
01:38:56.000 --> 01:38:57.583
I have just reunited with my daughter.

874
01:38:59.458 --> 01:39:01.083
I don't want her to lose her loved ones.

875
01:39:03.418 --> 01:39:04.668
I beg you.

876
01:39:05.543 --> 01:39:08.082
Can you let go of this grudge?

877
01:39:08.083 --> 01:39:10.168
When you killed my parents.

878
01:39:11.668 --> 01:39:13.542
I lost my loved ones.

879
01:39:13.543 --> 01:39:15.417
What about that?

880
01:39:15.418 --> 01:39:20.249
Thirty years later. you have turned
the whole world into a bloody mess.

881
01:39:20.250 --> 01:39:23.083
You must pay for the sins you sowed!

882
01:40:25.293 --> 01:40:26.625
How could it be you?

883
01:40:29.583 --> 01:40:30.918
Qiao.

884
01:40:33.125 --> 01:40:34.708
I'm sorry.

885
01:40:38.043 --> 01:40:39.458
I cannot...

886
01:40:40.583 --> 01:40:42.833
let you kill Duan Zhengchun.

887
01:40:47.125 --> 01:40:48.458
Because...

888
01:40:50.250 --> 01:40:52.500
he's my father.

889
01:40:54.750 --> 01:40:55.958
You are so silly.

890
01:41:02.875 --> 01:41:04.250
Qiao.

891
01:41:05.925 --> 01:41:07.132
you had...

892
01:41:08.250 --> 01:41:10.293
already saved my life.

893
01:41:13.418 --> 01:41:15.293
So don't blame yourself.

894
01:41:17.168 --> 01:41:18.668
You are so silly.

895
01:41:21.168 --> 01:41:23.708
To die in your arms.

896
01:41:26.793 --> 01:41:28.293
I have...

897
01:41:31.277 --> 01:41:34.234
no regrets in my life.

898
01:41:34.235 --> 01:41:35.569
It is my fault.

899
01:41:41.458 --> 01:41:42.958
Qiao.

900
01:41:46.833 --> 01:41:51.625
Will you still take me to the countryside?

901
01:41:54.043 --> 01:41:55.043
Yes.

902
01:41:57.418 --> 01:41:58.458
I will.

903
01:43:19.458 --> 01:43:21.750
[Xing]

904
01:43:32.833 --> 01:43:35.668
I didn't want this for her.

905
01:43:37.625 --> 01:43:39.168
Azhu!

906
01:43:47.125 --> 01:43:51.042
Thirty years ago. I was in Dali.

907
01:43:51.043 --> 01:43:52.833
I had never been to Yanmen Pass.

908
01:43:57.458 --> 01:43:59.250
As for the letter you mentioned.

909
01:44:02.875 --> 01:44:04.917
I didn't write it.

910
01:44:04.918 --> 01:44:07.293
Nor am I the leading brother you seek.

911
01:44:17.125 --> 01:44:18.500
I really don't understand.

912
01:44:20.168 --> 01:44:22.583
Why did they use you to kill me?

913
01:44:50.750 --> 01:44:52.293
[Haiyi]

914
01:44:53.000 --> 01:44:54.000
[Hongchang]

915
01:45:21.500 --> 01:45:22.500
Bai Shijing!

916
01:45:23.750 --> 01:45:27.458
The Dog Beating Staff is a powerful object.

917
01:45:28.625 --> 01:45:32.375
It should choose a wise master.

918
01:45:34.043 --> 01:45:37.167
The Beggars' Gang is the
largest gang in the world.

919
01:45:37.168 --> 01:45:39.832
yet it serves the weakened Song dynasty.

920
01:45:39.833 --> 01:45:45.499
Mr. Murong said that if Great
Song waged war with Dali.

921
01:45:45.500 --> 01:45:47.999
the world would be in chaos.

922
01:45:48.000 --> 01:45:50.292
The world would be in chaos.

923
01:45:50.293 --> 01:45:53.375
Then... we will have a
chance to rise to power!

924
01:45:55.333 --> 01:45:58.167
So you used me to kill Duan Zhengchun!

925
01:45:58.168 --> 01:45:59.417
All along.

926
01:45:59.418 --> 01:46:04.875
you and Kang Min were being influenced by
Murong Fu behind the scenes to cause chaos!

927
01:46:06.333 --> 01:46:11.293
The world has descended to chaos
because of shameless people like you!

928
01:46:16.333 --> 01:46:18.168
Did she have a part in killing my sister?

929
01:46:20.708 --> 01:46:24.167
Kang Min. how can you
face the Beggars' Gang?

930
01:46:24.168 --> 01:46:25.917
How can you face Vice Master Ma?

931
01:46:25.918 --> 01:46:27.083
Ma Dayuan?

932
01:46:28.458 --> 01:46:30.458
He abducted me when I was 14!

933
01:46:32.543 --> 01:46:36.543
My whole life was ruined
by the Beggars' Gang's men.

934
01:46:37.793 --> 01:46:39.375
But I won't be resigned to this fate.

935
01:46:41.411 --> 01:46:43.371
I want all the men in the world...

936
01:46:44.418 --> 01:46:46.168
to bow and scrape to me.

937
01:46:46.918 --> 01:46:49.958
If it is something that I cannot have.

938
01:46:51.333 --> 01:46:53.543
I won't let anyone else have it either.

939
01:46:54.875 --> 01:46:57.780
What makes you think
that all men will listen to you?

940
01:46:59.333 --> 01:47:01.168
My beautiful face.

941
01:47:02.000 --> 01:47:04.749
Except for Qiao Feng.

942
01:47:04.750 --> 01:47:09.582
all the men in the world fall at my feet.

943
01:47:09.583 --> 01:47:12.208
Even your father is no exception.

944
01:47:16.668 --> 01:47:19.500
Your face certainly is pretty.

945
01:47:43.458 --> 01:47:44.793
My face!

946
01:47:56.292 --> 01:47:59.332
Elder Bai. Qiao Feng has arrived.

947
01:47:59.333 --> 01:48:01.709
Thank you. You have fulfilled your mission.

948
01:48:07.083 --> 01:48:09.207
Mr. Murong.

949
01:48:09.208 --> 01:48:13.500
after killing Qiao Feng.
we can share the world.

950
01:49:24.543 --> 01:49:27.418
Murong Fu. you finally show yourself.

951
01:49:28.418 --> 01:49:30.707
Today. we must settle all grudges!

952
01:49:30.708 --> 01:49:34.874
Today is the day the Great
Yan will be restored.

953
01:49:34.875 --> 01:49:39.082
You can either be a Great Yan hero

954
01:49:39.083 --> 01:49:42.582
or a dead Song soldier.

955
01:49:42.583 --> 01:49:47.917
If you don't surrender.
I'll take your life here.

956
01:49:47.918 --> 01:49:49.583
Come and take it if you dare!

957
01:49:50.543 --> 01:49:51.543
What are you waiting for?

958
01:49:54.333 --> 01:49:55.417
Scumbag!

959
01:49:55.418 --> 01:49:56.668
Look at your hand!

960
01:50:47.292 --> 01:50:48.624
Why haven't you left yet?

961
01:50:48.625 --> 01:50:49.957
I'm not leaving!

962
01:50:49.958 --> 01:50:51.874
This is none of your business.

963
01:50:51.875 --> 01:50:52.918
Go home.

964
01:50:54.793 --> 01:50:55.793
Go!

965
01:50:55.794 --> 01:50:57.417
I'm here to help you!

966
01:50:57.418 --> 01:50:58.999
I brought my father's sword.

967
01:50:59.000 --> 01:51:00.000
Take it.

968
01:52:51.292 --> 01:52:53.666
I cannot believe a Khitan

969
01:52:53.667 --> 01:52:58.792
would use a broken sword of Dali
to defend the debilitated Song.

970
01:53:00.168 --> 01:53:01.749
Can you defend it?

971
01:53:01.750 --> 01:53:05.042
I'm defending not only this land.

972
01:53:05.043 --> 01:53:06.958
but also the righteous way of the world!

973
01:54:05.293 --> 01:54:06.957
Do you see?

974
01:54:06.958 --> 01:54:10.168
This is what happens
if you don't submit to the Great Yan.

975
01:54:49.918 --> 01:54:52.249
Do you think that your
Eighteen Subduing Dragon Palms

976
01:54:52.250 --> 01:54:54.874
is the most powerful martial arts skill?

977
01:54:54.875 --> 01:54:59.625
Our Murong family's Star Shifting
surpasses all other martial arts skills.

978
01:55:00.875 --> 01:55:02.624
Qiao Feng.

979
01:55:02.625 --> 01:55:05.583
haven't you always been
obsessed with being a hero?

980
01:55:07.000 --> 01:55:10.832
But now. that notion
must be shattered. right?

981
01:55:10.833 --> 01:55:15.625
You couldn't have expected to end up
with no family and a gruesome death.

982
01:55:21.000 --> 01:55:23.749
If you cling on to a thought.

983
01:55:23.750 --> 01:55:26.292
then you are trapped by a thought.

984
01:55:26.293 --> 01:55:30.999
Let go of a thought
and be freed of distracting thoughts.

985
01:55:31.000 --> 01:55:34.249
Only then can one become a Buddha.

986
01:55:34.250 --> 01:55:39.749
Master. why is there a Lowered-brow
Bodhisattva and an Angry-eye Vajra?

987
01:55:39.750 --> 01:55:42.667
Angry-eye Vajra's obsession
is to get rid of demons.

988
01:55:42.668 --> 01:55:46.167
Then is this obsession right or wrong?

989
01:55:46.168 --> 01:55:47.625
Should one let go of it?

990
01:56:16.707 --> 01:56:20.082
Murong Fu. I'm not a hero.

991
01:56:20.083 --> 01:56:23.292
I'm just an ordinary person
who holds fast to the right path.

992
01:56:23.293 --> 01:56:26.543
What I must do today is send you to hell!

993
01:59:12.168 --> 01:59:16.292
Your father finally brought
your mother and Azi back to Dali.

994
01:59:16.293 --> 01:59:19.168
But you know your mother
can't stand your father.

995
01:59:19.875 --> 01:59:23.599
It didn't take long before
she returned to Mirror Lake.

996
01:59:25.043 --> 01:59:26.793
And then there is Azi.

997
01:59:29.583 --> 01:59:31.083
She's a naughty girl.

998
01:59:32.583 --> 01:59:34.333
She said she wanted to roam the world.

999
01:59:35.500 --> 01:59:38.083
She has disappeared now.
I don't know where she has gone.

1000
01:59:42.043 --> 01:59:45.793
I promised to bring you to the countryside.

1001
01:59:46.708 --> 01:59:48.333
We are here now.

1002
01:59:51.500 --> 01:59:53.875
Just like I told you before.

1003
01:59:56.333 --> 01:59:58.208
I'll herd cattle and you'll herd sheep.

1004
01:59:59.500 --> 02:00:01.083
We will pay the world no mind.

1005
02:00:08.293 --> 02:00:10.218
Across all the kingdoms in the world...

1006
02:00:11.250 --> 02:00:12.668
and thousands of autumns.

1007
02:00:14.833 --> 02:00:16.168
in my heart.

1008
02:00:17.958 --> 02:00:19.625
there is only you. Azhu.

1009
02:00:28.543 --> 02:00:36.543
[In Memory Of My Beloved Wife. Azhu]

1010
02:02:10.833 --> 02:02:12.125
Qiao Feng!

1011
02:03:16.625 --> 02:03:18.124
Father?

1012
02:03:18.125 --> 02:03:19.958
You're still alive.

1013
02:03:22.500 --> 02:03:24.624
I hid from the world for 30 years

1014
02:03:24.625 --> 02:03:29.082
just to wait for the day
when you can restore our Great Yan.

1015
02:03:29.083 --> 02:03:30.999
How can you be so useless?

1016
02:03:31.000 --> 02:03:34.250
I'm sorry. Father!

1017
02:03:35.083 --> 02:03:36.750
I. Murong Bo. am back.

1018
02:03:38.418 --> 02:03:40.293
This is just the beginning.

1019
02:04:12.875 --> 02:04:15.375
Yuanshan. are we near Yanmen Pass yet?

1020
02:05:52.875 --> 02:05:55.167
Thank you for raising my son.

1021
02:05:55.168 --> 02:05:56.168
Who are you?

1022
02:06:01.216 --> 02:06:02.383
Who did this?

1023
02:06:05.500 --> 02:06:09.875
Xiao Yuanshan. I can
finally return this to you.

1024
02:06:39.958 --> 02:06:41.668
Xiao Yuanshan.

1025
02:06:43.793 --> 02:06:45.583
Thirty years have passed.

1026
02:06:48.750 --> 02:06:51.125
You have finally shown yourself.

1026
02:06:52.305 --> 02:07:52.917
Watch Online Movies and Series for FREE
www.osdb.link/lm
